<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">In stages following fire, or other unnatural disturbance, <i>Encelia farinosa </i>may dominate alone as an alliance for several years before <i>Larrea tridentata </i>and other long-lived shrubs re-establish.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
